summary: adds a relatively large quest to obtain artifacts left behind by the aedra and daedra princes
descriptionHtml:
adds a brand new quest to the game, which at the end of the quest you are awarded multiple artifacts one for every daedric prince and aedra. this is my first mod so please no negative comments

Bugs: (i pretested this for bugs)
-daedric bow takes the appearance of the tytanis retext origin unknown
-Daedric armor set the gloves and helmet appear to be normal steel gauntlets and steel helmet, dont really know how to fix this
-one of the artifacts dont appear in the right hand, but it does work in the left hand, no clue why this happens
